 UHECRs,\nthe astrophysical neutrino fluxes exhibit a significant (factor of a few)\nreduction compared to the na\\\"ive superposition of free nucleons for sources of\nUHECR nuclei with a populated cascade. The numerical code implementing the\nmodel has been made publicly available, which facilitates the integration of\nour results in similar frameworks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Apr 2019 22:18:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2019 12:19:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 20 Sep 2019 20:06:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-11"}
